HEADWORD: Desiccant
<hw>De*sic"cant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>desiccans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>desiccare</ets>. See
<er>Desiccate</er>.]</ety> <def>Drying; desiccative.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A medicine or application for
